{"TopicId":187315,"ForumId":148,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal Space Program 2: Master Post","CreatedByName":"sh1pman","CreatedById":147869,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T23:28:00Z","PageNum":5,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Cataclism","CreatedById":191188,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:46:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP2 is the VERY BEST gaming announcement of 2019!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nTHANK YOU, developers!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n..........\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nP.s.: I KNOW it might be too soon for that but, as you guys did with KSP1, please make KSP2 available on GOG as well!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-19T19:48:52Z\u0022 title=\u002208/19/2019 07:48  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 19, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Cataclism\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"norwayschnitzel","CreatedById":199506,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:46:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have tears in my eyes, this was my childhood.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DodoOnTheM\u00FCn","CreatedById":182844,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:46:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan i get my crafts that i build in KSP 1 to transfer over to KSP 2? I\u0027ve made a lot of stock and modded crafts in the over 2000 hours i have in the game and i would find it sad to lose those in the new game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:46:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653221\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566243965\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187694\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xurkitree\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Xurkitree said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP 1.9 CONFIRMED YAHOOOO!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere? I haven\u0027t seen anything about that, only KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:46:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaven\u0027t popped in here in ages - but damn I\u0027m excited for this. Seems to be incredibly promising from what I see so far. Will definitely be picking it up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:46:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653204\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566243483\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022148056\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022T1mo98\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, T1mo98 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill the classic parts shown in the trailer be updated to look more like their revamped looks\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNah, let\u0027s have the iconic versions.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hold3ngold3n","CreatedById":197497,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:46:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen Can I Pre-Order?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Yakuzi","CreatedById":85181,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:47:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThese 2 images from the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://store.steampowered.com/app/954850/Kerbal_Space_Program_2/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Esteam page of KSP2\u003C/a\u003E make me particularly excited, it really looks like infrastructure/processing is going to be a thing, and I especially like the grimy industrial feeling of the second pic:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00220BTXyi7.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/0BTXyi7.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00222UPF8ks.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/2UPF8ks.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nN.B. looks like these pics are from in-game footage, could be wrong though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: it also looks like robotics are included based on the rotating habitation ring in the trailer\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-19T20:00:29Z\u0022 title=\u002208/19/2019 08:00  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 19, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Yakuzi\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frank_G","CreatedById":100000,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:47:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am in total awe... watched the trailer about 10 times before even thinking about visiting the forums. I am in for the journey! \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Omer Ran","CreatedById":199504,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:48:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653219\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566243941\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257805\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StarManta\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, StarManta said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe announcement post mentions a pair of binary planets, so there\u0027s SOME level of upgrades from the current system. I\u0027d be surprised if it was true N-body, but I\u0027m not gonna rule out being surprised.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d be happy enough with a 3-body physics so we can have cool stuff like Lagrange points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StarManta","CreatedById":57805,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:48:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653224\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566243981\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182844\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DodoOnTheM\u00FCn\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, DodoOnTheM\u00FCn said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan i get my crafts that i build in KSP 1 to transfer over to KSP 2? I\u0027ve made a lot of stock and modded crafts in the over 2000 hours i have in the game and i would find it sad to lose those in the new game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, they\u0027re making a clean break. If they supported backwards compatibility they wouldn\u0027t be able to do half the new stuff they\u0027re planning.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"releansol","CreatedById":153963,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:48:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe will see. Surprized but not hyped.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starkos","CreatedById":199507,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:48:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill KSP 2 run on Google Stadia?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"norwayschnitzel","CreatedById":199506,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:48:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have tears in my eyes, this was my childhood.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aelipse","CreatedById":197170,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:48:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have so many thoughts and feelings right now, but I\u0027m gonna boil\u00A0them down to just four words: Guys, I love you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-19T19:48:54Z\u0022 title=\u002208/19/2019 07:48  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 19, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Aelipse\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"UomoCapra","CreatedById":167737,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:50:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653126\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566242205\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002285576\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MD5Ray01\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, MD5Ray01 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m honestly hoping that we don\u0027t get Metro Exodus\u0027d and have the game get turned into an EGS exclusive before it launched on Steam.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe game will be released on Steam and other digital storefronts, as well as\u00A0Xbox\u00A0Marketplace and PlayStation Store.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Caelib","CreatedById":59329,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:50:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes. Yes. Yes. Yes. Yes!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starkos","CreatedById":199507,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:50:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll the images look amazing, but I feel like it won\u0027t run in my computer with onboard GPU. KSP 1 barely runs on it, but I love it. If it runs on Stadia, graphics shouldn\u0027t be a problem for poor computers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-19T19:51:13Z\u0022 title=\u002208/19/2019 07:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 19, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Starkos\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"1of6Billion","CreatedById":46191,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:50:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the words of the great philosopher H. Simpson: Whoohoo!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"UomoCapra","CreatedById":167737,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:51:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653228\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566244007\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197497\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Hold3ngold3n\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Hold3ngold3n said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen Can I Pre-Order?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStay tuned for more information on this at a later time\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Raptor9","CreatedById":67915,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:51:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002266485\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SQUAD\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0I\u0027m still processing all of this, however if there is one thing I would ask for (even though I know you aren\u0027t making KSP 2, but you talk to Star Theory apparently), is that KSP 2 be available to play \u003Cstrong\u003Ewithout an internet connection\u003C/strong\u003E.\u00A0 That is one thing that has ruined a lot of games for me.\u00A0 I travel a lot, and when I bring my gaming laptop with me, KSP is one of the few games I can still play without an internet connection.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the meantime, I look forward to continuing playing KSP 1.8 and beyond. I salute you.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Iamsodarncool","CreatedById":138967,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:51:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTechnical question: is KSP2 developed with the legacy GameObject Unity architecture, or with ECS/Jobs?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RockyTV","CreatedById":57161,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:52:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653242\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566244207\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167737\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022UomoCapra\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, UomoCapra said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe game will be released on Steam and other digital storefronts, as well as\u00A0Xbox\u00A0Marketplace and PlayStation Store.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat doesn\u0027t mean anything. That\u0027s what Deep Silver said before accepting Epic\u0027s deal and turning Metro into an EGS exclusive days before the official release.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReleasing it on digital storefronts is a thing. But can we expect it to be available on Steam on launch day?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have a bad feeling about this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aaodon","CreatedById":185176,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:53:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTwo old boys are back!!! Cannot wait for them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EKerbal Space Program\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EMicrosoft Flight Simulator\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:53:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653226\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566244001\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022142607\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022legoclone09\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, legoclone09 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaven\u0027t popped in here in ages - but damn I\u0027m excited for this. Seems to be incredibly promising from what I see so far. Will definitely be picking it up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell good to see you again. You going to stick around this time? \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}